                        <interp inst="t18490129-name-426" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN SIMMS</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman</hi>). I produce a certificate of the prisoner's con vic<lb></lb>tion—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted June</hi>, 1847, <hi rend="italic">and confined six</hi> months)—I was present—he is the person.</p>
